About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • Double Convenience: Ugreen USB to Dual Micro USB Cable is able to charge two electronic devices with Micro USB 2.0 interface simultaneously or transfer the data between computer or tablet with standard USB port and android smart phones without plugting and unplugting the phone frequently to protect the micro USB jack on them.
  • Fast Charge & Data Sync: 480Mbps max data transfer speed for each micro usb plug of Ugreen Micro USB 2.0 Splitter Y Cable; 2.4A max charging speed for both micro USB plug used simultaneously, 2A max charging speed for only one micro USB plug used. (Note: the total current output will be 2.4A max when charging 2 devices simultaneously.)
  • Universal Compatibility: Used to charge any 2 devicec equipped with a micro USB 2.0 interface, including Samsung Galaxy smartphones and tablets, HTC One and Motorola Droid smartphones, Windows tablets, Bluetooth headset, keyboard, speaker, PlayStation 4, Xbox One controller, GPS devices, Nexus 7 tablets, Amazon Kindle (Kindle Fire, Kindle Fire HDX, and Kindle Paperwhite), PSP game console and other portable devices.
  • Excellent Design&Premium Quality: Made of Tin-plated 2228AWG thick 100% oxygen-free copper conductor with shileding and low resistance inside, and high-grade aluminum housing outside, Ugreen Micro USB to USB Cable is able to ensure the data transfer and power delivery in high level. The cable offers a slim Micro USB connector molding that plugs into your device even with an outer slim case on.
  • Reliable&Durable Performance: 24K Gold-plated connectors can bear 10000 times Swap tests and 10000 Bend lifespan. Durable, flexible and environmentally friendly TPE cable jacket protects wire cores from resists kinks and tangles. Heat-resistant.

Product description

Size:3FT

Ugreen Micro USB Y Splitter Cable
This cable features a standard Type-A USB connector on one end and two Micro Type-B connector on the other. For example, you can plug the Type-A connector into your computer, then plug the Micro Type-B connector into one or two devices with a Micro Type-B port. Devices like mobile phones, smartphones, MP3 players, tablets, digital cameras and digital camcorders often have Micro Type-B ports.

Product Features
Support data sync speed of 480 Mbps totally
Support charging speed up to 2.4A in total when charging 2 devices simultaneously and around 2A max for only use one micro usb port.
Plug and Play, no driver installation needed
2228AWG Oxygen-Free Copper conductor and Gold-plated connector with low resistance for stable and better signal transfer
With Aluminum housing design to ensure minimum signal loss effectively
With flexible and environmentally friendly TPE cable jacket protecting wire cores from resists kinks and tangles. Heat-resistant.

Compatible List
Samsung Galaxy Smartphones
Android Phones from other Manufacturers like Motorola, Huawei, Google, Blackberry, LG & HTC
Most Android Tablets like the Samsung Tabs and the Amazon Fire
PSP Controllers
Power Banks or Portable Batteries
Portable or Bluetooth Speakers
MP3 Players
Digital Cameras and Camcorders
Any other device that charges through a micro usb cable

What's in the pacakge
1x Ugreen Gold-plated USB 2.0 A Male to Micro B Data Sync and Charging Cable

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

MarilynTop Contributor: Firefly (TV Show)
5.0 out of 5 stars Simple solution to keep two mobile devices connected to charge off one USB port...
Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2017
Verified Purchase
The UGREEN Micro USB Splitter Cable USB 2.0 to Dual Micro USB Y-Split Cable (1.5ft) works nicely for connecting two micro USB devices to one USB port. The cable is just the right length without having too much extra slack to require bundling up the cable with a cord organization tie. Even the cable itself is pretty durable being made from a thick TPE outer cable jacket to keep it from kinking or tangling. I haven't tested the speed with data transfer specifically as I've mainly purchased this cable for keeping two small devices powered, but it does recognize the device to allow a data transfer when plugging in my mobile device. I opted to pick up this cable for my car as the stereo has a built in USB port that can allow music to play from a small sized GB thumb drive or provide direct power to a connected device. This allows me to keep my mobile device and Bluetooth audio transmitter charged for complete hands-free driving when needing to use my navigation app to locate the best commute to-and-from work or even locating a new restaurant. It's a simple cable solution that keeps my main console area clear from clutter.

3.0 out of 5 stars Description wasn't totally forthcoming.
Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2019
Size: 3FTVerified Purchase
This cable is fine if you want to just charge two low-draw devices without unplugging one or the other. This is fine if you want to send data from a computer to one device or the other. But it does not pass power between the micro connectors, nor does it pass data between the two micro connectors. The description made it sound like it did this, but when I got mine, I found out otherwise. Should have bought the cheap Y cables that do exactly that.
